= Transition Model =

(% class="box warningmessage" %)
(((
**Current Status: Phase 1 (Alpha / Founder Mode)**
FactHarbor is currently in an early setup phase. Processes described here are being established.
)))

== 1. Purpose ==

The Transition Model explains how FactHarbor evolves from an early experimental phase to a more stable organisation and, eventually, to a federated ecosystem.

== 2. Phases (Illustrative) ==

* **Phase 1: Alpha (Founder Mode)** – Current phase. Very small core team; focus on validating the basic approach and achieving multi-agent debate reliability. The Founder inhabits multiple operational domains.
* **Phase 2: Beta (Verein Mode)** – Legal incorporation complete. More users and community members; governance and processes become clearer and more formal. Separation of Legal (Board) and Operational (Domains) roles begins.
  * **Current Status:** Verein founded on 23 April 2026. Commercial Register filing submitted on 27 April 2026; entry letter received on 29 April 2026; UID assigned: `CHE-448.446.098`. Public SHAB / Zefix visibility may still be pending. See [[Legal Framework>>FactHarbor.Organisation.Legal and Compliance.Legal Framework.WebHome]].

* **Phase 3: Release 1.x (Scale Mode)** – Stable operation, documented contributor processes, and full separation of roles with dedicated domain leads.
* **Phase 4: Federated Phase** – Multiple instances or partners adopt the model; shared governance principles across a network.

== 3. Founder Mode Role Mapping (Phase 1) ==

To maintain progress during the startup phase, roles are mapped as follows:

|=Governance Layer|=Role / Domain|=Phase 1 (Current)|=Phase 2 (Target)
|**Legal (Verein)**|**President**|Robert Schaub|Elected Member
|**Legal (Verein)**|**Treasurer**|Stefanie Schaub-Hehr|Elected Member
|**Operations**|**R&D Domain**|Robert Schaub|R&D Lead
|**Operations**|**Operations Domain**|Robert Schaub|Operations Lead
|**Operations**|**Partner & User Relations Domain**|Robert Schaub|Relations Lead
|**Operations**|**Finance Domain**|Robert Schaub|Finance Lead

**Transition Status:** The Swiss Verein was founded on 23 April 2026 with President (Robert Schaub) and Treasurer (Stefanie Schaub-Hehr). Commercial Register filing was submitted on 27 April 2026; the entry letter was received on 29 April 2026; UID `CHE-448.446.098` is assigned. Phase 2 transition is underway, while public SHAB / Zefix visibility may still be propagating.

== 4. Transition Principles ==

* Preserve mission and neutrality during growth.
* Document which responsibilities move from individuals to shared bodies.
* Make role changes and new structures transparent to community members and users.
* Keep early experimental material accessible as historical context.

== 5. Practical Use ==

This page is intentionally lightweight. More detailed transition plans and roadmaps will be held in project management tools or dedicated XWiki pages when needed.
